name: Photoblend
description:
A merge of photorealism loras. Uses Flashlight Photography, RZ Analog 1.5, epiNoiseOffset v2, and Film Grain v2, I did not keep track of the weightings used. Doesn't seem to have a nsfw bias. Recommended weighting is 0.4-0.7.

Presented as-is with no support or explanation beyond the above.
